00:52:47,020 --> 00:52:50,535
and I commented and said, you know,

680
00:52:50,860 --> 00:52:52,816
"Damn, this guy's pretty good
at playing possum."

681
00:52:52,940 --> 00:52:55,295
'Cause I know I'd be howling 
like a, you know,

682
00:52:55,420 --> 00:53:00,096
whatever with this riding up my crotch
like his jumpsuit was.

