695
00:53:47,620 --> 00:53:50,896
And I was like,
"Whoa, what happened to this guy?"

696
00:53:51,020 --> 00:53:53,898
And then one of his eye was open.

697
00:53:54,020 --> 00:53:59,936
So I kind of, like, did the thing like Pierce
